{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be clean and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Global Financial Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #2c3e50; /* Darker blue-grey */\n            color: #ecf0f1; /* Light grey for text */\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #3498db 3px solid; /* Brand blue accent */\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        #hero {\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/3498db/ffffff?text=Financial+Excellence') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 500px;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.7); /* Brand blue overlay */\n        }\n        #hero .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #services h2, #about h2, #contact h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        .service-item, .about-content, .contact-form {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #3498db; /* Brand blue */\n        }\n        .about-content {\n            background: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .about-content p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: #3498db; /* Brand blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            border: 0;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background: #2980b9; /* Darker brand blue */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #2c3e50; /* Darker blue-grey */\n            color: #ecf0f1;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Global Financial Solutions</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Empowering Your Financial Future</h2>\n            <p>Expert advice and strategies for sustainable growth.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Investment Strategy</h3>\n            <p>Tailored investment plans to meet your unique financial goals.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Risk Management</h3>\n            <p>Identifying and mitigating financial risks for stability.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Wealth Planning</h3>\n            <p>Comprehensive strategies for long-term wealth creation and preservation.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <p>Global Financial Solutions is a leading consultancy dedicated to providing innovative and reliable financial guidance. With a team of seasoned professionals, we are committed to helping our clients navigate the complexities of the financial world and achieve their objectives.</p>\n                <p>Our mission is to foster financial well-being through expert analysis, personalized strategies, and unwavering integrity.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-form\">\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Global Financial Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}